Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:07.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.00,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He intends only his own gain,\N他所盤算的只是他自身的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.09,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he is in this,\N而在此場合下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.63,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as in many other cases,\N像在其他許多場合一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:21.22,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,led by an invisible hand to promote an end\N他在無形之手引導下所促成的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:24.35,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which was no part of his intention.\N而這個結果並非出自於他的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.85,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nor is it always the worse for the society\N其本意也不總是對社會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.31,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that it was not part of it.\N造成不利的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.00,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：引自經濟學之父亞當·斯密所著的《國富論》第4篇第2章。）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:13.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:19.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是金融街的中心  Midas銀行廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:28.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Asset  也就是個人資產
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:34.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Deal中可以幫助Entre作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:34.36,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：Entre、Entrepreneur，即創業者。）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:35.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:36.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:42.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面顯示的是Deal的對手的資產數據
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及所持株數
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.49,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（株：想運用Asset必須附上相關的十株，株是類似於Asset靈魂之物。株擁有\N獲得Asset支配權以及獲得股息的功能，是創業者在金融街中賴以生存的重要道具之一。）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:45.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:49.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entre每週必須參加一回名為「Deal」的對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這既是權利也是義務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:53.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  去參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:57.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他那個樣子夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.80,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:03.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副連蟲子都不敢殺的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:05.06,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:06.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭一把嗎?

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,----Title
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.61,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}暗合

Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:43.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先用手掃過卡的表面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:01.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M… 真朱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真朱? 不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一樣是新人  請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的Asset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.51,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Asset (資產)：Midas銀行發放給Entrepreneur用來輔助其進行Deal的存在，\N根據Entrepreneur的資質化為人型或者怪物型等各種不同的姿態。）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺和對方的比起來 差距好大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asset是表現Entre未來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種意義之下差異並不代表不公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  之後就請加油吧  那麼我撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是我的未來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛… 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能不要發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開打了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.57,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Open  Deal」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.07,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Open  Deal」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:43.83,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Micro：給Asset投資一定的資金而產生的經濟魔法(Flation)，\N經濟魔法包括「Micro」「Mezzo」「Macro」。）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:43.83,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.63,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Direct：是戰鬥方式的一種。可以直接從對方Entrepreneur身上\N獲取利益，而自己遭受的損失則更為巨大。）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.63,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真朱!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:58.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉古!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你至少得自己保護自己  否則可是會破產的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破產?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:11.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所持有的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險  不要伸出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然兩次都失誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  吉古!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Micro  30萬!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.38,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷勢沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話  當然痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙完全搞不清楚狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這老手也覺得新人難對付嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧  反正和我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:17.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你被幹掉了  一切就都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是節約點兒上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉古  Micro  90萬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.72,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和對手說我們不幹了  他一定能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解你個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:38.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真朱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂… 喂  真朱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我了  你快點藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:54.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是損失啊  你還要繼續?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:10.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是囂張的Asset
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉古  300萬  Micro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.35,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老手游刃有餘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹田崎嗎  真是無聊的Deal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  對於情報屋來說可是不可多得的Deal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:32.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是徹底的外行  也有生存下來的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這真是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:40.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三國先生  您是最有體會的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:45.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:47.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不了多久就能好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  因為我的關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的Entre可不會有這樣的擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有人受傷的話  會擔心是正常的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和剛剛那和人都好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到攻擊的話  資金會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消耗資金  採取攻擊才能獲得利益
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然搞不清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧  戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:35.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真朱!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會恢復的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉古  最後一擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Micro  500萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.57,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公縻  快投資  刷卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:07:59.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mezzo  Flation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:00.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000萬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:00.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續投資!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:01.79,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Mezzo Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mezzo  Flation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000萬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:06.71,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Scorched  Earth」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scorched  Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mezzo  Flation可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都覺得好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:10.65,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Closing」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:15.83,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You  have  gain\N您獲得了盈利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真朱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你獲得了勝利  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問這個  我是在問你真朱怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指Asset的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:31.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們馬上就會見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  關於下回Deal的指名…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:48.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余賀?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來累得不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  這次破例送你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優秀的新人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沾了Asset的光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢  三國先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:03.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是為那個小子加油了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎誤會了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多久沒這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被捲入Deal之中的傢伙莫名獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏了呢  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:26.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是沒有否定那個人獲勝的可能性而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:33.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一無所知的情況下參加Deal卻獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自你之後  他是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:40.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那個時候您也打算要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為像我一樣的人嗎  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  無法推測
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:10:59.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那傢伙還特地來看Deal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:06.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧

Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在做夢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為第一次Deal您這可真是了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先來享受一下勝利的余悅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑  誰要享受啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:42.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這邊世界來說  消耗的僅僅是移動所需的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會妨礙到日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周後  我再來迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要拚死戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像之前那樣就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢也請隨便用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:03.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒說不要外傳  但別人大多不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要聲張是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  通過Midas卡可以和Asset對話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:12.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的時候就請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:14.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對話?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪  怎麼沒說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.77,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.64,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  傷都好了  現在正在進行恢復訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:30.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:33.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個普通的Asset而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的話  一般都會擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只有這件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  暫且是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那若是有什麼事情就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用「喂喂」的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這也看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  怎樣才能停止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破產的話  就會被驅逐出金融街
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為這個結果  在這個世界裡過於殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:13.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是奉勸您老實地繼續Deal　而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會覺得世界變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:29.00,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記取錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:28.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.37,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:39.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個  十  百… 三千三百五十萬日元!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:43.09,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't really value the concept of low risk\N…並不看重低風險概念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:44.55,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you understand?\N你們明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.26,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that in turn can mean no interest...\N就是說  低風險反過來意味著無利潤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  今天吃得很豪華啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課的時候沒有學習  很少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  只是有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到提款卡什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:03.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  羽奈日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:06.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有一千萬  你會怎麼用?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:07.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時代  一切都不知道會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一發生什麼事  不存點錢的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:19.67,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在埼玉縣埼玉市  因涉嫌將兩歲三個月大的兒童窒息致死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.63,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琦玉縣警方將二十四歲的母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:21.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是不知道會變成什麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是佩托恩公司達拉斯會長贈送的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十九年陳釀嗎  很捨得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:37.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長是希望能趕走福克斯·麥克納馬拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:41.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算利用我  使對手企業落敗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  那個公共事業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地人強烈反對  現在政權的態度也很消極
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民就是沒有長遠的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投向公共不行的話  投往民間也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:53.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  要把資金流動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  個人消費一點兒也沒有增長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是我們  大家都束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不只是日本  這是世界性的趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是能力範圍之外的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意個人消費
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就儘管讓他們存錢好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  潮流會發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻  遲早會到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這一點是毋庸置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余賀公縻  十九歲  平成經濟大學的二年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭環境好像比較複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外  就沒什麼特別的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突出的優點和缺點都沒有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該很慌張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有弄錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是流行的玩具?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一千日元而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是一千日元而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您別跟我開玩笑了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這個人好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總共二百三十八日元  找您七百六十二日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:14.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裝入袋子裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  還沒睡醒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 等下  你看到了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:24.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:27.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:28.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是一千日元嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.23,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是混在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.73,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過你現在能看出來了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得這麼直接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人渾身不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.15,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家不都這樣用著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.91,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這邊全都是黑色的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  資金從金融街流入到一般世界裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.91,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用的話  會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.71,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢  我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不想Deal你快點決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entre再不想打仗至少也得每週一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我消耗的也很厲害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:20.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.60,Asset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之贏了就行了  你好好考慮考慮吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  收您一萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找您九千八百零三日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:00.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  那裡不是有五千日元紙幣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼全部都是一千日元的紙幣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝起來錢包不就變得很厚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個… 有點髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很乾淨的紙幣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人  請冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:13.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:15.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這語氣算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫店長出來  店長!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張錢就行  給我那張!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你說的  給你這張錢就滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你滿意了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要後悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能讓你那破臉從我眼中消失  這夠便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這是謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:58.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近手頭有點寬裕  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工啊  得做到很晚很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不習慣黑色的錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你的Deal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對經驗豐富的老手  你做得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那傢伙的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:34.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從金融街回來的人  便能分辨出黑色的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Midas  money
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Midas銀行發行的紙幣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:41.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Midas  money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:42.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用這個錢也不會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:51.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那傢伙說要用未來作為擔保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢就會有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  是做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話  算是花錢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是使用大筆資金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利的話  你也會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大筆金錢什麼的  我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺著普通的錢  建立普通的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:13.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通就可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的人追求普通  有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逃避戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拘泥於普通的人說的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是討厭輸掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你父親那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:39.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就會生氣  也就說明你想逃避你父親的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃避  要注視著你自己的潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:48.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都有生在這個世界的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:51.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當個普通人不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:58.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是三國壯一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:07.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有這樣的想法  說不定能幫你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著你啊  在那條街上

